    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 33,888₽ | 物品价值: 19,500 | Mechanic报价: 10,920₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 25,350₽\n购买渠道 @ Skier 等级4 < 22,425₽\n\nPSR是一款由AWC Silencers制造的效果优异的.338 LM (8.6x70)膛口制退器。它能够降低后坐力，抑制枪口抬起。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 33,888₽ | 物品价值: 19,500 | Mechanic报价: 10,920₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 25,350₽\n购买渠道 @ Skier 等级4 < 22,425₽\n\nPSR is an effective muzzle brake manufactured by AWC Silencers for .338 LM (8.6x70). Reduces recoil and counters the muzzle rise. The brake is threaded and compatible with AWC PSR Thor sound suppressors."
    },
